Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,叫可卡因\N{\rEng}It's called cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Right.
