Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真不是闹着玩的\N{\rEng}No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下午4点  股市已经暴跌了508个点\N{\rEng}By 4:00 p.m., the market had dropped 508 points.
