Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我可以和你妻子谈\N{\rEng}Yes, I will talk to your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我  别接电话\N{\rEng}Trust me, do not answer the phone.
