Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.13,1:30:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想我一辈子也想不通是为什么\N{\rEng}But for the life of me, I can't figure out why.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.01,1:30:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们是有点不正统\N{\rEng}I know we're a little unorthodox,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.47,1:30:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做事有点大张旗鼓\N{\rEng}we're a little loud in the way we do things.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.26,1:30:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你得理解\N{\rEng}But you gotta understand,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.47,1:30:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是新入行的  你懂\N{\rEng}we're the new guys on the block, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.02,1:30:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在努力让自己名扬万里\N{\rEng}we're trying to make a name for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.23,1:30:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但我希望你明白  我们不做违法的事\N{\rEng}But I want you to understand, we don't do anything illegal.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.65,1:30:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何也不做\N{\rEng}Whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.82,1:30:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去找证监会的人\N{\rEng}I mean, you could talk to the SEC.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.44,1:30:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他们过去六个月来我办公室拜访了十五次\N{\rEng}They were at my office 15 times over the last six months.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.57,1:30:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我没...我没什么要隐瞒的\N{\rEng}I mean, I got... I got nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.28,1:31:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道证监会只是个民事管理机构\N{\rEng}Well, you know the SEC is a civil regulatory agency.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.12,1:31:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们查的是犯罪活动\N{\rEng}We pursue criminal activities.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.74,1:31:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,正是这样  你要查的是真正的犯罪\N{\rEng}Exactly! You go after real criminals,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.16,1:31:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我很好奇你们为什么会调查我\N{\rEng}which makes me wonder what the hell you're investigating me for?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.33,1:31:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  说实话...\N{\rEng}I mean, honestly...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.75,1:31:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们做过什么或者在做什么吗\N{\rEng}what is it that you think that we did or do?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.54,1:31:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\rEng}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.71,1:31:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\rEng}Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.05,1:31:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,乔丹  我不能讨论正在进行的调查\N{\rEng}Look, Jordan, I can't discuss an ongoing investigation.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.55,1:31:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  我明白  没事的  我理解\N{\rEng}No, I get that. No, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.35,1:31:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这么说\N{\rEng}With that said...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.60,1:31:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,其实这案子是被扔在我桌上的\N{\rEng}this case got dumped on my desk...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.52,1:31:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-是这样吗  -你懂的  高层\N{\rEng}- Did it? - You know, by a higher-up
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.43,1:31:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那些想要作秀的人\N{\rEng}who needs to make a show
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.55,1:31:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,得借着追查一家新公司为由\N{\rEng}of looking into the new company on the block,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.73,1:31:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-拉上一堆媒体之类的  -新上位那些\N{\rEng}- with all the press and everything. - New loud guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.31,1:31:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就变成了来做调查的蠢货\N{\rEng}And then I end up being the schmuck who does the looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.94,1:31:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\rEng}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.94,1:31:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只是  你懂的...这东西很烦\N{\rEng}It's just, you know... it bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.95,1:31:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是新人\N{\rEng}We're the new guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.58,1:31:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是去敲华尔街的门的人\N{\rEng}We're the one that's banging on Wall Street's door.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.57,1:31:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  你应该...\N{\rEng}I mean, you should...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.74,1:31:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该去查查那些大投行在干什么\N{\rEng}You should see what's going on at the bigger firms.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.74,1:31:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我说  我知道所有的内幕\N{\rEng}I mean, I know all the information.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.37,1:31:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的  高盛  雷曼兄弟  美林\N{\rEng}It's true! Goldman, Lehman Brothers, Merrill...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.37,1:31:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}均为美国大投行
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.25,1:31:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,担保债务凭证\N{\rEng}Collateralized debt obligations?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.37,1:31:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么互联网概念股\N{\rEng}This Internet stock bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.71,1:31:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就是他妈的放屁\N{\rEng}I mean, it's a fucking travesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.59,1:31:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我能手把手地告诉你\N{\rEng}I could take you step-by-step
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.83,1:31:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们每一步都在做什么\N{\rEng}through what exactly is occurring.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.84,1:31:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要开口问\N{\rEng}All you have to do is ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.59,1:32:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我随时恭候\N{\rEng}I'm available.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.05,1:32:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我就等你这句话了\N{\rEng}That's exactly what I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.51,1:32:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白像这样的谈话\N{\rEng}I don't see why a little sitdown like this
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.27,1:32:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么就不能对我们双方都有利了\N{\rEng}can't be profitable for the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.93,1:32:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就应该这样  是吧\N{\rEng}It should. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.91,1:32:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这本来就该对我们双方都有利\N{\rEng}It should profit the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.27,1:32:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-是应该这样  -听着\N{\rEng}- It should. - Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.31,1:32:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给你我的私人号码\N{\rEng}I'm gonna give you my personal line.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.61,1:32:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,工作日里随时可以打电话给我\N{\rEng}Five days a week, you just call me, feel free.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.74,1:32:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-我会的  -棒极了\N{\rEng}- I'll do that. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.03,1:32:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们确定不喝点什么\N{\rEng}Are you sure you guys don't want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.78,1:32:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不饿吗  什么也不要\N{\rEng}You're not hungry? Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.54,1:32:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么都不要吗  不要吗  -不用了\N{\rEng}- Nothing? No? - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.29,1:32:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让我问你几个问题\N{\rEng}Let me ask you,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.19,1:32:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你不想透露太多个人信息\N{\rEng}and if you don't wanna get too personal,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.96,1:32:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以随时叫我闭嘴\N{\rEng}just tell me to shut up at any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.13,1:32:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是曾经考虑过弄个经纪人执照\N{\rEng}Did you try to get your broker's license at one time?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.84,1:32:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道自己有没有听错\N{\rEng}Did I hear that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.76,1:32:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是也曾想来华尔街分一杯羹\N{\rEng}Were you trying to take a stab at Wall Street?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.59,1:32:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有吗  -你和谁谈过话\N{\rEng}- No? - Who you been talking to?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.60,1:32:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈和谁谈过了\N{\rEng}Who the fuck you been talking to?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.68,1:32:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在调查我  我也听了你的事迹\N{\rEng}Well, you're investigating me. I hear things.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.52,1:32:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂我意思吧\N{\rEng}You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.69,1:32:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有想过假如你坚持下去了\N{\rEng}You ever think about what would've happened
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.35,1:32:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,会发生什么\N{\rEng}if you would have stayed the course?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.23,1:32:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  每当我搭地铁回家\N{\rEng}You know what? When I'm riding home on the subway
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.15,1:32:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋都他妈汗湿了\N{\rEng}and my balls are fucking sweating,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.49,1:33:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一套西服连续穿了三天...\N{\rEng}I'm wearing the same suit three days in a row...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.36,1:33:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我当然想过\N{\rEng}Yeah, you bet I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.95,1:33:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前就想过这个  谁不想呢  是吧\N{\rEng}I've thought about it before. Who wouldn't, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.70,1:33:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  谁他妈会不想呢\N{\rEng}Right, who fucking wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.83,1:33:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么...\N{\rEng}What do you get...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.08,1:33:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一个私人为题  你不用回答\N{\rEng}Another personal question, no need to answer...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.41,1:33:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  没关系的  乔丹\N{\rEng}No, that's all right, Jordan.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.87,1:33:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你能赚多少啊  五六万之类的\N{\rEng}What do you pull in? 50, 60K? Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.04,1:33:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一年吗  大约\N{\rEng}A year? In the ballpark?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.13,1:33:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\rEng}Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.67,1:33:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样说吧\N{\rEng}Let's put it this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.55,1:33:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,局里至少能给你一把免费的枪\N{\rEng}You get a free handgun when you sign up for the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.09,1:33:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈让我很生气啊  你懂我意思吗\N{\rEng}No, but it fucking pisses me off. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.30,1:33:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你想想  那些建设了这个国家的人\N{\rEng}You think about the people that built this country,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.55,1:33:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,像你一样勤勤恳恳的人\N{\rEng}hardworking people like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.06,1:33:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,消防员  老师  联邦探员\N{\rEng}Firefighters, teachers, FBI agents.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.73,1:33:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,结果到最后\N{\rEng}End of the day,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.34,1:33:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群人在经济上被生吞活剥了\N{\rEng}you guys get fucking skinned alive financially.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.48,1:33:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈让我太生气了\N{\rEng}It fucking makes me angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.44,1:33:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如今  关于华尔街和这个市场\N{\rEng}Now the one thing about Wall Street and this market is,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.61,1:33:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来  我觉得\N{\rEng}for me, I feel
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.36,1:33:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,能回馈社会是好事  你知道  有些\N{\rEng}it's good to give back. You know, there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.78,1:33:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有些情况下我能\N{\rEng}There are situations where I can
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.03,1:33:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让这些人处境好点  明白吗\N{\rEng}make those situations better for people. You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.66,1:33:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂我意思的\N{\rEng}You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.04,1:33:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,机遇\N{\rEng}Opportunity
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.75,1:33:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一切\N{\rEng}is everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.08,1:33:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太对了\N{\rEng}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.46,1:33:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,举个例子  有这么个小孩  是吧\N{\rEng}Take for example, I got this one kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.00,1:34:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去学校学环境科学之类的\N{\rEng}Went to school for environmental science, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.88,1:34:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但却被学生贷款困住了\N{\rEng}He was bogged down by student loans.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.76,1:34:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他妈又要做三重心脏搭桥手术\N{\rEng}Turns out, his mother needed triple bypass surgery.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.55,1:34:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-天呐  -没错  很惨\N{\rEng}- Jesus. - Right. Horrible situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.06,1:34:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.10,1:34:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们在正确的时候\N{\rEng}But we got him into the market
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.27,1:34:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,拉他入市  再选一只正确的股票\N{\rEng}at the right time and chose the right stock.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.06,1:34:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给予他正确的指导\N{\rEng}We gave him the right guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.89,1:34:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,轰  一夜之间  就改变了他整个人生\N{\rEng}Boom! Overnight, changed his entire life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.19,1:34:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈被送进了纽约最好的医院\N{\rEng}Got to put his mother into the best hospital in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.61,1:34:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是没用\N{\rEng}It didn't work out for her,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.77,1:34:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,假设  她还是去世了  很不幸\N{\rEng}granted, she passed away, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.57,1:34:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们至少给了他那个机会\N{\rEng}But we gave him that opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.57,1:34:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂我在说什么吗\N{\rEng}You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.45,1:34:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这取决于建立一个好团队\N{\rEng}It's just about setting up the right team,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.76,1:34:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一夜之间你的人生将得以改变\N{\rEng}and then overnight your life can change.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.34,1:34:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一个实习生能...能...\N{\rEng}What does... What does an intern...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.30,1:34:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一个实习生做这样一单能赚多少\N{\rEng}What does an intern make in a deal like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.26,1:34:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在那种情况下\N{\rEng}Well, in that situation,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.22,1:34:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在那笔特定的交易里  就那一笔\N{\rEng}in that particular trade, and it was one trade,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.60,1:34:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,五十多万美元吧\N{\rEng}north of half a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.73,1:34:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我会为任何人做这件事  明白吗\N{\rEng}And I'd do that for anybody, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.06,1:35:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,任何需要适当的指导的人\N{\rEng}anybody that needs the proper guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.54,1:35:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,能再说一遍吗  就把刚刚说的再说一遍\N{\rEng}Can you say that again, just the way you said it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.05,1:35:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一模一样的\N{\rEng}Just the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.97,1:35:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂你在说什么\N{\rEng}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.14,1:35:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧  你当然懂我在说什么\N{\rEng}Oh, come on! You know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.48,1:35:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得刚刚乔丹在干的事是...\N{\rEng}I think what Jordan just did is he...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.56,1:35:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-假如我没弄错的话...  -不是\N{\rEng}- If I'm not mistaken... - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.77,1:35:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚在试图贿赂一个联邦官员\N{\rEng}...you just tried to bribe a federal officer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.98,1:35:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  理论上我没有贿赂任何人\N{\rEng}No, technically I didn't bribe anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.15,1:35:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  我听到的可不是这样的  乔丹\N{\rEng}No, no, that's not the conversation I heard, Jordan.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.65,1:35:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  根据美国刑法\N{\rEng}No, no, according to the U.S. criminal code,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.24,1:35:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,贿赂必须有个\N{\rEng}there needs to be an exact
