Dialogue: 0,2:45:47.02,2:45:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有跟你说过那个账户的事\N{\rEng}about that account?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:48.29,2:45:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fs20\fn方正静蕾简体\frz336\b0\pos(161,194)\c&H424245&}别说对自己不利的话\N\N\N\N我戴着窃听器呢
Dialogue: 0,2:45:54.61,2:45:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得的\N{\rEng}You remember.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:55.73,2:45:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多有四五百万的  对吧\N{\rEng}It was like four or five mil, something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:57.82,2:46:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该要退还四五百万  对吧\N{\rEng}He was supposed to kick back four or five mil, was it?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:05.37,2:46:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上  我那个时候\N{\rEng}Actually, I was...
Dialogue: 0,2:46:06.91,2:46:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我那时候嗑药磕得一团糟  乔丹\N{\rEng}I was fucked up, Jordan,
Dialogue: 0,2:46:08.37,2:46:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-所以我什么都不记得了  -是啊\N{\rEng}- so I don't really remember. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:09.96,2:46:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  你个傻瓜\N{\rEng}Yeah, right. Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:12.63,2:46:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他打来  你就通知我  好吗\N{\rEng}Well, if he calls you, you make sure and contact me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:18.46,2:46:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-当然了  -好\N{\rEng}- Yeah. Of course. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:20.22,2:46:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  当然\N{\rEng}Of course, yeah. No, of course.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:25.72,2:46:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,最后那块黄狮鱼你还吃不吃  伙计\N{\rEng}You gonna eat that last piece of yellowtail, bud?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:29.27,2:46:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃了  都给你吧\N{\rEng}No, it's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:31.85,2:46:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我能蘸这个吗\N{\rEng}Can I get this?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:35.69,2:46:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  还有什么……\N{\rEng}So, what else is...
Dialogue: 0,2:46:40.15,2:46:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,内奥米和其它一切都还好吗\N{\rEng}Well, how's Naomi and everything?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:42.24,2:46:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道\N{\rEng}You know how it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:43.74,2:46:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在恨死我了\N{\rEng}She hates my fucking guts.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:47.58,2:46:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,希尔迪怎么样  她还好吗\N{\rEng}How's Hildy? Good?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:50.08,2:46:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她还活着  所以活的也很糟\N{\rEng}She's still alive, so my life is fucked, you know?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:53.75,2:46:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:01.76,2:47:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,乔丹先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Jordan.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:04.93,2:47:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,乔丹先生  有客人找您\N{\rEng}Mr. Jordan, you got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:07.47,2:47:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:08.97,2:47:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有客人找您\N{\rEng}You've got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:26.28,2:47:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你马上穿好衣服\N{\rEng}I need you to get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:28.37,2:47:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  这是搞什么\N{\rEng}Why? What the fuck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:35.62,2:47:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去蹲监狱了\N{\rEng}You're going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:49.35,2:47:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:50.64,2:47:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我去穿衣服\N{\rEng}I'll get some clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:52.31,2:47:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们帮你\N{\rEng}We'll give you a hand with that.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:03.24,2:48:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:16.54,2:48:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局\N{\rEng}FBI!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:18.21,2:48:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人坐下\N{\rEng}Everybody sit down.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:19.39,2:48:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,把手举起来  不许出声\N{\rEng}Put your hands where they can be seen, and shut up!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:21.88,2:48:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的别碰我\N{\rEng}Don't you fucking touch me.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:23.67,2:48:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的放开我\N{\rEng}Get your fucking hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:25.88,2:48:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不许离开你们的座位\N{\rEng}Don't get out of your seats!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:40.86,2:48:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈的可是香奈儿\N{\rEng}It's fucking Chanel!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:55.12,2:48:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我告发了所有人\N{\rEng}I gave up everyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:57.37,2:48:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,作为回报\N{\rEng}And in return,
Dialogue: 0,2:48:58.96,2:49:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我在内华达的一个我从来没听说过的\N{\rEng}I got three years in some
Dialogue: 0,2:49:00.57,2:49:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼地方蹲了三年\N{\rEng}hellhole in Nevada I'd never even heard of.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:05.21,2:49:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我父亲疯狂麦克斯曾经说过的\N{\rEng}Like my pops, Mad Max, had said,
Dialogue: 0,2:49:08.38,2:49:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"恶有恶报"\N{\rEng}"The chickens had come home to roost."
Dialogue: 0,2:49:12.39,2:49:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,随便他什么意思吧\N{\rEng}Whatever the fuck that means.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:18.19,2:49:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望法官大人认同\N{\rEng}I hope Your Honor would agree
Dialogue: 0,2:49:19.56,2:49:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尔福先生在跟联邦调查局合作方面\N{\rEng}that Mr. Belfort has distinguished himself
Dialogue: 0,2:49:21.65,2:49:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有出色的表现\N{\rEng}in terms of his cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:23.82,2:49:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在贝尔福先生的协助下\N{\rEng}Mr. Belfort has helped the government win convictions
Dialogue: 0,2:49:25.94,2:49:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,政府给二十四余名重罪犯定了罪\N{\rEng}of over two dozen serious offenders
Dialogue: 0,2:49:29.74,2:49:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,并且追回了成百上千万美金\N{\rEng}and helped them recover millions of dollars
Dialogue: 0,2:49:31.74,2:49:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,用以补偿受害者\N{\rEng}to be made available for restitution to their victims.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:37.41,2:49:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,法庭对被告的判决为\N{\rEng}The sentence of the court shall be
Dialogue: 0,2:49:38.85,2:49:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在联邦监狱关押三十六个月\N{\rEng}36 months in federal prison.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:42.92,2:49:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请把被告押回去\N{\rEng}Please remand the defendant.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:47.26,2:49:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:51.89,2:49:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rEng}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:07.80,2:50:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fs23\fn方正大标宋简体\c&H292021&\pos(207,84)\frz0.105}斯特拉顿·奥克蒙特  贝尔福获刑
Dialogue: 0,2:50:41.31,2:50:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认  当我们到监狱的时候\N{\rEng}I'm not ashamed to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:43.81,2:50:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我快吓死了\N{\rEng}When we arrived at the prison,
Dialogue: 0,2:50:45.73,2:50:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得这有什么丢人的\N{\rEng}I was absolutely terrified.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:48.69,2:50:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尔福  站起来\N{\rEng}Belfort, on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:50.15,2:50:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但实际上我用不着害怕\N{\rEng}But I needn't have been.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:52.65,2:50:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么很短的一瞬间\N{\rEng}You see, for a brief fleeting moment,
Dialogue: 0,2:50:55.99,2:50:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了自己曾富得流油了\N{\rEng}I'd forgotten I was rich.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:59.04,2:51:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而我住在消费的世界里\N{\rEng}And I lived in a place where everything was for sale.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:05.00,2:51:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道不想学一下怎么把它们卖掉吗\N{\rEng}Wouldn't you like to learn how to sell it?
Dialogue: 0,2:51:07.79,2:51:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了  我这辈子见过不少混蛋\N{\rEng}So listen. I've met some bad motherfuckers in my life.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:10.76,2:51:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,摇滚明星  专业运动员  黑帮分子\N{\rEng}I'm talking about rock stars, professional athletes, gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:14.30,2:51:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是一些坏得透顶的混蛋\N{\rEng}I'm telling you, some real bad motherfuckers.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:16.18,2:51:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这家伙  我的好朋友\N{\rEng}But this guy, my good friend,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:18.56,2:51:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,乔丹·贝尔福先生真的是\N{\rEng}Mr. Jordan Belfort, is the single
Dialogue: 0,2:51:21.39,2:51:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子遇见过的最最最最最坏的混蛋了\N{\rEng}baddest motherfucker I have ever met.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:24.73,2:51:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我现在希望你们\N{\rEng}So I want you right now
Dialogue: 0,2:51:26.52,2:51:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,向我的好朋友  世界上最棒的销售员\N{\rEng}to give a warm Auckland, New Zealand welcome
Dialogue: 0,2:51:29.73,2:51:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,献上新西兰奥克兰最诚挚的欢迎\N{\rEng}for my good friend and the world's greatest sales trainer,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:34.20,2:51:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有请乔丹·贝尔福先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Jordan Belfort!
Dialogue: 0,2:51:47.42,2:51:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:11.69,2:52:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,向我推销这支笔\N{\rEng}Sell me this pen.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:17.99,2:52:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是……\N{\rEng}It's...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:20.33,2:52:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一支很棒的笔\N{\rEng}It's an amazing pen.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:22.41,2:52:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对于专业人士来说  这是一支……\N{\rEng}For professionals, it's a...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:27.71,2:52:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,向我推销这支笔\N{\rEng}Sell me this pen.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:30.42,2:52:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是支好笔\N{\rEng}Well, it's a nice pen.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:31.71,2:52:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以用这支笔\N{\rEng}You can use the pen
Dialogue: 0,2:52:33.09,2:52:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,记下生活的点点滴滴  这样一来你就能\N{\rEng}to write down thoughts from your life so you can...
